<p><a href="http://www.dizzyd.com/blog/">Dizzy</a> gave his talk on <a href="http://www.passel.org/">Passel</a> this morning at <a href="http://conferences.oreillynet.com/os2005/">OSCON</a> and did a fine job. I&#8217;d say there were about 30 people there, the room was nearly full, questions were good, discussion was productive. Unfortunately Diz ran out of time and didn&#8217;t get a chance to demo Passel for the assembled throng. But we did have some good follow-on discussions after his talk.</p>
