<p>While I was away over the weekend, Dizzy <a href="http://www.dizzyd.com/blog/?p=57">unveiled Passel</a>, the open identity technology I&#8217;ve been <a href="http://www.saint-andre.com/blog/2005-05.html#2005-05-02T21:12">hinting at</a> for the last few months. It&#8217;s really Dizzy&#8217;s baby, I just helped out with the <a href="http://www.passel.org/whitepaper.html">whitepaper</a> (which has a few consistencies and needs to be beefed up in a few areas &#8212; will do that this week). More on Passel soon.</p>
